#1 Tab is 4 spaces
#2 The "{" is placed below the function, struct, enum, etc
#3 Code should be readable without scrolling to the right on a 1920*1080 screen
#4 Clusters of operations (assigning struct variables, declaring a series of related functions), should be column aligned
#5 Temporary comments are preceded by '//', permanent comments should be inside '/* */' tags
#6 Function scoped variables are declared at the begining of the function